timeline.bodyText:
You need to change this to something like this:
Literal date1 = vf.createLiteral("2019-09-02", XMLSchema.DATE);
Literal date2 = vf.createLiteral("2018", XMLSchema.GYEAR);
assertTrue(cmp.compare(date1, date2) < 0);

In strict mode, QueryEvaluationUtil will throw an exception. ValueComparator catches this exception, falls back to doings its own comparison, and orders them in alphabetical order on datatype.
In other words: by choosing the values and datatypes of our two literals very carefully, we make sure that strict mode will give a different comparison result than non-strict mode.

